    Protos.Transaction.Pool
    Protobuf enum wallet.Transaction.Pool This is a bitfield oriented enum, with the following bits: bit 0 - spent bit 1 - appears in alt chain bit 2 - appears in best chain bit 3 - double-spent bit 4 - pending (we would like the tx to go into the best chain) Not all combinations are interesting, just the ones actually used in the enum.
